# ✨ UI/UX PRO MAX & NUMBER FORMATTING RULES
- **Glassmorphism**: Replace Brutalism (`border-2 border-slate-900`) with glass effects (`bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-md border border-slate-100/slate-200 shadow-xl`).
- **Input Fields**: DO NOT use thick borders for `.input-premium`. Use 1px slate borders, soft shadows, and blue/teal outline on focus.
- **Floating Cards (StatCard)**: Ensure cards do not "blend" (hòa) into the background. Use subtle top-borders (`border-t-4`) grouping with colors (indigo/emerald) and deep shadows (`shadow-xl`) to increase contrast.
- **Numbers (Counts/Totals)**: ALWAYS zero-pad small counts to 3 digits using `.padStart(3, '0')` (e.g. `001`, `003`) to maintain high aesthetics.
- **Numbers (Currency/Financials)**: Always use the `<CurrencyInput>` component or `.toLocaleString('vi-VN')` for displaying money.

